  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>The Hotel Alpen Roc is available on a half board basis which includes breakfast and dinner, afternoon snacks and an 'unlimited drinks' package which includes a variety of drinks between 10am -10.50pm.</p>
<p>Fuel up for a day on the slopes with the continental breakfast buffet with additional hot options, available from 7 - 10am (times subject to change)</p>
<p>Enjoy evening meals which are served buffet style with additional hot food prepared to order, available from 7 - 9pm (times subject to change). <span>The dishes are made from fresh local products, and you can enjoy a variety of dishes including traditional cuisine. </span></p>
<p>Make the most of unlimited drinks from 10am - 10.55pm. The package includes a range of sodas, fruit juices, hot drinks, beer and wine. You can also enjoy tea time cake and aperitifs at the bar from 6 - 10.55pm.</p>
<p>Christmas and New Year gala dinners included</p>
<p> </p>]]></cateringDescription>
